    {
      "id": "39",
      "name": "角色推薦",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 28,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Ganyu_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "甘雨",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "甘雨作為以重擊作為特色的弓箭角色，十分契合該武器的技能效果（二層蓄力第二段傷害能穩定受到3層提升效果），且甘雨自身天賦、雙冰元素共鳴、冰四件套都能提供暴擊率，使得該武器",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "副詞綴不會被太過弱化。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 15,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yoimiya_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "宵宮",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "宵宮是比較多使用普通攻擊的角色，該武器注重普通攻擊和重擊，可以作為宵宮五星武器中的一個選擇。但它的弱點是，需要與敵人拉開距離才能讓傷害最大化，但是拉開距離容易使弓箭射空，在實戰中還需要旅行者斟酌一下距離上的問題。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 38,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Fischl_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "菲謝爾",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "站場流菲謝爾的傷害類型中，普攻佔比較大，作為五星武器，該武器能提供高額的",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "攻擊力加成",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，如果能控制好距離去吃滿層數，該武器也是比較合適的選擇。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
